contract.recitals:
WHEREAS, the Parties desire to explore a potential partnership for AI-powered analytics platform development (the “Purpose”);
WHEREAS, in connection with the Purpose, each Party may disclose to the other certain Confidential Information (as defined below);
WHEREAS, the Parties wish to set forth the terms and conditions governing the use and protection of such Confidential Information.
NOW, THEREFORE, in consideration of the mutual promises and covenants contained herein, and for other good and valuable consideration, the receipt and sufficiency of which are hereby acknowledged, the Parties agree as follows:

WHEREAS, Disclosing Party possesses certain non-public, confidential, and proprietary information relating to its business, technology, products, operations, finances, and plans;
WHEREAS, Receiving Party desires to receive and review certain Confidential Information (as defined below) solely for the purpose of evaluating a potential seed investment opportunity (the "Purpose");
WHEREAS, the Parties desire to set forth the terms and conditions under which Receiving Party may receive, use, and protect such Confidential Information;
NOW, THEREFORE, in consideration of the mutual covenants and promises contained herein, and for other good and valuable consideration, the receipt and sufficiency of which are acknowledged, the Parties agree as follows:

WHEREAS, the Company desires to obtain financing from the Investor, and the Investor desires to provide financing to the Company, on the terms set forth in this SAFE;

WHEREAS, this SAFE is intended to be a “simple agreement for future equity,” under which the Investor’s investment may convert into equity of the Company upon certain events, as provided herein;

WHEREAS, the parties intend that this SAFE be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of California, and that any disputes be resolved in the venue specified herein.

WHEREAS, Disclosing Party possesses certain confidential and proprietary information relating to its business, technology, products, and services;

WHEREAS, Receiving Party desires to receive certain Confidential Information (as defined below) from Disclosing Party for the purpose of evaluating potential seed investment opportunity (the "Purpose");

WHEREAS, Disclosing Party is willing to disclose such Confidential Information to Receiving Party, subject to the terms and conditions set forth in this Agreement;

NOW, THEREFORE, in consideration of the mutual covenants and agreements hereinafter set forth and for other good and valuable consideration, the receipt and sufficiency of which are hereby acknowledged, the Parties agree as follows:

WHEREAS, Company is engaged in the business of software and application development and desires to engage Contractor to perform certain professional services as described herein;

WHEREAS, Contractor is a skilled professional with expertise in full-stack software development, including React Native, Node.js, and AWS technologies, and desires to perform such services for Company;

WHEREAS, the Parties wish to establish the terms and conditions under which Contractor will provide such services to Company;

NOW, THEREFORE, in consideration of the mutual covenants and agreements hereinafter set forth and for other good and valuable consideration, the receipt and sufficiency of which are hereby acknowledged, the Parties agree as follows:

WHEREAS, the Investor desires to provide funding to the Company in exchange for the right to certain shares of the Company's capital stock, subject to the terms and conditions set forth herein;

WHEREAS, the Company desires to accept such funding and issue such rights to the Investor on the terms set forth herein;

WHEREAS, this SAFE is one of a series of SAFEs issued by the Company to investors (collectively, the "SAFEs") on substantially similar terms;

NOW, THEREFORE, in consideration of the mutual covenants and agreements set forth herein and for other good and valuable consideration, the receipt and sufficiency of which are hereby acknowledged, the parties agree as follows:

WHEREAS, Client is engaged in the business of providing creative services and desires to engage Freelancer to perform certain UX/UI design services in connection with its e-commerce platform;

WHEREAS, Freelancer is a professional UX/UI Designer with the requisite skills, experience, and expertise to perform such design services;

WHEREAS, Freelancer desires to provide such services to Client on the terms and conditions set forth herein;

WHEREAS, the Parties wish to establish the terms and conditions under which Freelancer will provide the Services (as defined below) to Client;

NOW, THEREFORE, in consideration of the mutual covenants, promises, and agreements contained herein, and for other good and valuable consideration, the receipt and sufficiency of which are hereby acknowledged, the Parties agree as follows:
